<h2>SphereOptimize: Optimization on a Unit Sphere</h2>
<p>A simple tool for numerical optimization on the unit sphere. This is achieved by combining the spherical coordinating system with L-BFGS-B optimization. This algorithm is implemented in Kolkiewicz, A., Rice, G., &amp; Xie, Y. (2020) &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.jspi.2020.07.001">doi:10.1016/j.jspi.2020.07.001</a>&gt;. </p>
